announcementSubject: Microsoft Power BI Workshop Saturday 11th June - Please Register!!!
announcement:
Here’s a link to the registration form for SIT’s Power BI Dashboard In a Day training day taking place on June 11th from 9am to 5pm in the upstairs BIT lecture room. It would be greatly appreciated if students know about this training opportunity to gain hands-on experience with Microsoft Power BI.

 

It’s important that students register if at all possible before the event so that we can enable a Power BI free license for their account. Attendees will also need to install the Power BI Desktop application before the event, information on how to do this is available on the registration form.

 

After this workshop, attendees will better understand how to:

  • Connect to, import, and transform data from a variety of sources.
  • Define business rules and KPIs.
  • Explore data with powerful visualization tools.
  • Build stunning reports with Power BI.
  • Share dashboards with your team and business partners, and publish them to the web.


GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO GAIN NEW KNOWLEDGE/SKILLS TO PUT ON YOUR CV!
